title: Natural Resources, Mining, & Construction Employee Average Weekly Earnings, USA by State, January 2007-November2008
name: Natural Resources, Mining, & Construction Employee Average Weekly Earnings, USA by State, January 2007-November2008
description: This dataset, from the US Bureau of Labor Statistics, is part of a dataset that provides "All Employee Hours and Earnings". This dataset gives the total Natural Resources, Mining, & Construction average weekly earnings per state for each month from January of 2007 to November of 2008. The data for the states of West Virginia and Wyoming are for Natural Resources and Mining Employees only. Not all states are included due to lack of data.
